Package pl.put.poznan.buildinginfo.logic

Class Floor

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.put.poznan.buildinginfo.logic.Floor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ILocation
    public class Floor
extends Object
implements ILocation
    The Floor class represents a floor in a building. It contains information about the floor's ID, name, level, and a list of rooms. The class provides methods to calculate the volume, total area, total lighting power, and average lighting power density of the rooms on the floor.
